codex
The implementation and whitespace check are clean, but `npm test` cannot bind the pre-existing test server to `0.0.0.0` in this sandbox (`EPERM` before any endpoint runs). I’ll verify whether the intended loopback interface is permitted; if so, I’ll make that minimal test-helper correction so the required suite can execute without changing application behavior.
